	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Solve the Colony Vault puzzle. Let's be honest, you're not going to. But if you want to: &quot;goto 737 13 -110&quot; and interact with the mind flayer console.&#xD;&#xA;- Alternatively, just use &quot;oe COL_Vault_AutoSolve&quot; and the puzzle will solve itself and teleport you into place." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The party reacts to solving the mind flayer &quot;mind puzzle&quot; in the Colony Vault, near the Necro-Lab. Solving the puzzle unlocks a door where you can find the rewards." />
			<children>
